&ldquo;Digital Scholarship has released the Research Data Curation Bibliography. It includes over 100 selected English-language articles and technical reports that are useful in understanding the curation of digital research data in academic and other research institutions.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Most sources have been published from 2000 through 2011; however, a limited number of earlier key sources are also included.&rdquo;
View the Data Curation Bibliography.
A number of IASSIST members are cited in the bibliography.

